nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE QUICKLY UNRAVELING IN THE SUBTROPICAL CENTRAL PACIFIC...
summary: ...HENRIETTE QUICKLY UNRAVELING IN THE SUBTROPICAL CENTRAL PACIFIC... As of 5:00 PM HST Tue Aug 12 the center of Henriette was located near 35.3, -164.3 with movement NW at 18 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1001 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
